CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: FREYR Battery is an emerging producer of clean battery solutions for a better planet. It designs and manufactures high-density and cost-competitive lithium-ion batteries with a reduced carbon footprint for the global markets for electric mobility, stationary energy storage, marine and aviation applications.
